Package: easyML
Type: Package
Title: Easy Machine Learning Pipeline for Classification and Regression
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2026-02-21
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jose", "Ventura-Leon",
           email = "jventuraleon@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2996-4244"))
    )
Description: Simplifies machine learning workflows for classification and
    regression tasks. Provides a single function interface (easy_ml) that
    automatically handles preprocessing, model training, hyperparameter tuning,
    evaluation, and interpretability analysis. Includes sample size estimation
    tools (ml_sample_size) based on Monte Carlo simulation with power-law curve
    fitting, supporting multiple test partitions for robustness, bootstrap
    confidence intervals, and fit diagnostics. Features block-based and
    diversity-based train/test splitting for enhanced generalization assessment.
    Implements Random Forest, XGBoost, SVM, Neural Networks, and more using
    the tidymodels framework.
